text: You Only Live Once is a 1937 American crime drama movie directed by Fritz Lang and starring Sylvia Sidney, Henry Fonda, Barton MacLane, Jean Dixon, William Gargan, Jerome Cowan, John Wray. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1937 drama movies Category:1930s American crime drama movies Category:Movies directed by Fritz Lang
title: You Only Live Once
